	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>Action</strong> - Touch - 6th Level (Conjuration) - VSM (a sapphire worth 1,000 gp) - Permanent</p><p></p><p><strong>Utility</strong></p><ul><li><p>You touch an object weighing 10 pounds or less, whose longest dimension is 6 feet or less. The spell leaves an invisible mark on its surface and invisibly inscribes the name of the item on the sapphire used as the material component. Each casting requires a new sapphire.</p></li><li><p>At any time thereafter, you may take an Action to speak the itemâ€™s name and crush the sapphire. The item instantly appears in your hand, regardless of physical or planar distance, and the spell ends.</p></li><li><p>If another creature is holding or carrying the item, crushing the sapphire does not transport it. Instead, you learn who possesses the object and roughly where that creature is at that moment.</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.oZwKW3I3yzrSdpLE]{Dispel Magic} or a similar effect successfully applied to the sapphire ends this spell.</em></p>",
